Secure Logging

Assets / resources for which logging needs to be enabled or created - 
        APIs 
        web application
        server side code
        kubernetes
        PRs
        activities on image registry 
Using logging libraries like log4j
attributes of events and logs - time stamp, identity, action performed
what not to log
        passwords
        data elements that have regulatory or legal or statutory requirements like personally identifiable information or card holder data
log aggregation, log monitoring


